        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Connecting Minority Communities Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Office of Minority Broadband Initiatives, the Connecting Minority Communities Task Force, and the Connecting Minority Communities Pilot Program to facilitate, foster, and fund broadband internet access service and digital literacy in minority communities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
